'''Stephen Baker''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Tarron Neb]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the under 16 years old category. He was 16 at the time his entry was published.

